-- Bombay Dyeing's Wadia, Investors Plan to Sell Stake in Punjab Cricket Team
-- Anoop Agrawal
-- 2010-06-24T07:52:18Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-24/bombay-dyeing-s-wadia-investors-plan-to-sell-stake-in-punjab-cricket-team.html

          
          
             Bombay Dyeing & Manufacturing Co.
Joint Managing Director Ness Wadia and other owners of an Indian
cricket team are planning to sell their stake in Kings XI Punjab
and are talking to investors, Wadia told reporters in Mumbai
today.  
